name: BULL Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: We've structured our tokenomics with a few things in mind. Our pre-sale gives the project the funds it needs for a healthy launch without favoring pre-sale buyers so much that it undermines a healthy public launch. Team allocation is very small and is intended to ensure we have the firepower we need for a smooth delivery. Plenty of tokens have been allocated for community rewards, CEX/DEX liquidity, and ongoing marketing.
